### Genfeed API - Elements Aggregated Endpoint
### Get all element collections in a single request

########################################
# Get All Elements
########################################

### Get All Elements (Aggregated)
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/elements
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}

### Response includes:
# - cameras: Camera angle presets
# - moods: Mood presets
# - scenes: Scene presets
# - styles: Visual style presets
# - sounds: Sound effect library
# - blacklists: Content blacklists
# - lightings: Lighting presets
# - lenses: Lens type presets
# - cameraMovements: Camera movement presets

